data.description: A stunning, updated A-Frame on the perfect plot of land doesn't come for sale often! If you are looking for outdoor adventure--land, space, a babbling creek, then walking through this property will be the best thing you do all day! Imagine watching the snow fall in the great room with a crackling fire, cedar ceiling, and peaked front wall of windows. The amount of natural light in this home is unmatched!  The upper level loft will bring you right into the master bedroom. The main level has two more bedrooms with a bathroom. The walk-out lower level completes the home with two more bedrooms, laundry room, bathroom, and entertaining space. Words do not do this home justice. Come see for yourself!
